room_title: Escape room "X-Train" by Xterious Escape in Las Vegas

room_description: Your police unit has been dispatched to the train station to prevent a terrorist attack! You’ve cleared the station of civilians as best you can, but now it’s up to your team to thwart the attack! The terrorists have planned this well, do you have what it takes to stop them?
